ctional form of the resistance. {\textless}br{\textgreater}{\textless}br{\textgreater} We expect the application of our new TBC in land models will provide a consistent representation for the diffusive tracer exchange at the soil–air interface.{\textless}/p{\textgreater}{\textless}/p{\textgreater}},
